#write a program to print given year is leap year or not?

n=int(input("Enter year:"))
if((n%400==0&n%100!=0)or n%4==0):
    print(n,"It is a leap year")
else:
    print(n,"Not a leap year")

*********OUTPUT-1*********
Enter year:2003
2003 Not a leap year

*********OUTPUT-2*********
Enter year:2016
2016 It is a leap year
